<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtopcua-literaloperand.xml">LiteralOperand</db:link> is defined in OPC-UA part 4, 7.4.4.3. It contains a literal value that is to be used as operand for filters.</db:para>
<db:para>Setting the type should be done to match the expected types on the server. Otherwise the type will be guessed and may lead to errors because it does not match on the server.</db:para>
<db:programlisting language="cpp">import QtOpcUa as QtOpcUa

QtOpcUa.LiteralOperand {
    value: 43.21
    type: QtOpcUa.Constants.Double
}
</db:programlisting>
</db:section>
